title: "Identity Register"
---
# Identity Register

Identities in evan.network represent humans, organization or machines. 

Identities can be verified using the Identity Claim Service, accounts can be verified and gain trust explicitly from trustees or implicit from previous business relations.    


With on-behalf-of logic accounts can interact with a smart contract in the name of another account. Business scenarios where employees act in the name of a company  can be modeled securely in blockchain technology. 


